<p><code>dcl6</code> is being hosted in a separate repository: <a href="https://github.com/uhop/dcl6">https://github.com/uhop/dcl6</a> At the moment it is not on <code>npm</code>, so the only way to play with it is to clone the repo.</p>
]]></content>
